runs.name: B e h a v e

runRules: must play most up-to-date map version
runs must begin with a reset
timer, controls, speed and player name must be visible on HUD
shots fired in a previous run may not interfere with the current run
other players may not interfere with your run (holding doors open, weapon knockback)
mapRules: your map must be published on the game content server
your map should be arted (textured blockouts count as art)
your map name and thumbnail must match what is shown in-game
your map must be finished and no major changes are planned
you must keep admins informed about any breaking changes
